xhot_days <- wdw_metadata %>%
  select(DATE, WDWMEANTEMP) %>%
  filter(WDWMEANTEMP > 85)

  select(DATE, WDWMEANTEMP) %>%
  filter(WDWMEANTEMP > 79.8 & WDWMEANTEMP < 85)

  select(DATE, WDWMEANTEMP) %>%
  filter(WDWMEANTEMP > 71.3 & WDWMEANTEMP < 79.8)

  select(DATE, WDWMEANTEMP) %>%
  filter(WDWMEANTEMP > 62.8 & WDWMEANTEMP < 71.3)
